---
// Footer component following Vercel design system
---

<footer class="bg-canvas border-t border-hairline mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- About -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">About</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Free, privacy-focused background removal powered by AI. All processing happens in your browser - your images never leave your device.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Features -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Features</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-body">
          <li>✓ 100% Client-Side Processing</li>
          <li>✓ No Sign-Up Required</li>
          <li>✓ Unlimited HD Downloads</li>
          <li>✓ Batch Processing</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Technology -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3">Technology</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          Built with Astro.js and powered by Hugging Face Transformers using the Xenova/modnet model for high-quality image matting.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-hairline text-center text-sm text-mute">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} FreeRemoveBG. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .bg-canvas {
    background-color: var(--color-canvas);
  }
  
  .border-hairline {
    border-color: var(--color-hairline);
  }
  
  .text-body {
    color: var(--color-body);
  }
  
  .text-mute {
    color: var(--color-mute);
  }
</style>
